{"tid":808461,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"係咪處真係咁重要？","createTime":"2018-09-06T10:45:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-07T05:37:54.000Z","uid":125592,"like":137,"dislike":147,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"1b0d73d2ac7fe861e5e534f76f9832e37d4beba6","tid":808461,"uid":125592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T10:45:10.000Z","msg":"好多人尤其絲打探討呢個問題 <br />\n而加可以同你講 係好撚重要<br />\n我前任同現任都係咁樣<br />\n當你知道最愛嘅人係中學已經破左處果陣<br />\n係真係好唔開心 仲要可能係比垃圾臭mk抽插過<br />\n同前任拍拖果陣我仲係青頭<br />\n為左搵心理平衡真係諗過走去搵sp 揼邪骨破處<br />\n點知去到現任又係咁 唉<br />\n雖然我明過左去 大家都唔想<br />\n但見到佢就會凝住凝住有野 <br />\n之後開始鼻酸心酸 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望我可以睇開啲啦屌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/south_bear.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/south_bear.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以希望絲打們好好珍惜自己個處<br />\n如果一早無左就珍惜果個介意嘅男朋友<br />\n唔愛你 當你免費雞嘅話又有咩所謂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/poison.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d165cf38040d7402b9099e4455e9a8b79b2daba","tid":808461,"uid":41368,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T10:48:51.000Z","msg":"小多士入嚟未"},{"pid":"79e663f990d014ff3def39c84c07a3cd8bbe363d","tid":808461,"uid":125592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d165cf38040d7402b9099e4455e9a8b79b2daba","tid":808461,"uid":41368,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T10:48:51.000Z","msg":"小多士入嚟未"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T10:49:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a38227bbec5f668c0a989e6c7bd3d21aaadd798","tid":808461,"uid":131980,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T10:49:43.000Z","msg":"請原諒我的幼稚唔成熟傳統保守唔清高的情意結"},{"pid":"ba75424464883984d3aa5adcf4315ed0d2a0c996","tid":808461,"uid":178800,"like":42,"dislike":66,"score":-24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09